items.badge_description: The battle for grid iron supremacy is on. Who will be the victor? Who are we kidding, with your favorite brew and this badge, you've already won!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 70 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 15!

Youve pledged allegiance, and now its time to enjoy some beer! Now remember, not all American beer is fizzy and yellow. Thats 55 different beers from a brewery in the United States. Try 5 more for Level 12.
